1. User selects read button.
2. In the dialog box the user selects the .txt file that they would like to be encrypted.
3. User then selects the encrypt button and types in the name of the new encypted file.
4. Locate the .txt file and you will see it is encrypted.


1. To Decrypt, the user selects the read button.
2. Select the file that has been encrypted that you want to decrypt.
3. select the decrypt button.
4. Type in the name of the new file that is decrypted.
5. Locate the .txt file and you will see it is decrypted to its original state.
